- a. True
- b. False

### 54.
The airspace within 700 or 1200 feet of the surface (outside of airport or otherwise restricted airspace) is uncontrolled and designated as E or G and therefore appropriate for ultralight activity without specific permission.

- a. True
- b. False

### 55.
